CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 22, 1970, pg. 6 reads: "AUBA Youth Retreat - Ranch WLD (Where the Lord Dwells), at Fairview, Pa., near Erie, was the scene of the recent retreat, which was enjoyed by youth of the Allegheny-Union Baptist Association.  Mrs. Ruth West, adult advisor, looks on from the left, while the Rev. Rosamond C. Kay, president of the Christian Education Congress, checks a few pointers with youth leaders.  Continuing right, they are: Lee Ann Hart, Wayne Cooley, Adell McCall, Percy Jackson, Jo Ann Walker and Ruby Anderson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of young men and young women standing in front of church, possibly Nazarene Baptist, during Allegheny-Union Baptist Association youth retreat, Fairview, PA
